        <li><strong>Healthcare:</strong> Medical outreach, health education, and community clinics.</li>
        <li><strong>Agriculture:</strong> Farmer training, irrigation systems, and sustainable agriculture support.</li>
        <li><strong>Women Empowerment:</strong> Skills training, financial inclusion, and leadership development.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Development:</strong> Clean water, environmental protection, and local capacity building.</li>
